<p>Make the current thread sleep for a given duration. </p>
<p><a class="el" href="group__system.php#gab8c0d1f966b4e5110fd370b662d8c11b" title="Make the current thread sleep for a given duration.">sf::sleep</a> is the best way to block a program or one of its threads, as it doesn't consume any CPU power.</p>
